title: Excess of Paris Open Market Rate Over London Discount Rate on Three Month Bank Bills
notes: Source: Derived By NBER By Subtracting Series 13016 (London Open Market Rate, Three Month Bank Bills) From Series 13017 (Paris Open Market Discount Rate); Data Are From The Economist And The National Monetary Commission, "Statistics For Great Britain, Germany, And France, 1867-1908", P. 315-316.
